name: Love Boat
description:
Hello!

This lovely print is A5 seize and is printed on high quality 225 gsm paper.

It will be carefully packaged in a protective sleeve and will be shipped flat inside a stiff card backed envelope.

I will ship your order to the address you provide in the Etsy checkout – so please make sure it is correct. I'll send all orders to this address and not to your Paypal address.

If you have any questions about my work or if you'd like to commission custom pieces please get in touch with me! I'm happy to help! :)

Many thanks for looking! :)


© 2012 Gabriela Romagna

name: Happy Hugo
description:
Hello!

I posted a picture with all of them so you can see which colour combinations are available.

This little doggy is hand made by me and when you order one please let me know which one you'd like.

It's a nice small sized doggy which sits easily in your hand and measures approximately 7,5 cm tall, 5 cm width and 4 cm depth.

There is also the option to customise your doggy and chose a different belly and inner ear colour for a little extra fee of GBP 2.-

To avoid a misunderstanding I'd like to mention that GBP 9,90 is the price for one. I've chosen the picture with all of them so you see which ones are available :)

Also I'll add another colour soon and update the picture :) So check back! :)

Many thanks!
Gabriela
